extends java.lang.Object
    A stage of transaction, which is created by applying a single event (i.e. its message along with the context) to the entity.

    Invokes an event applier method for the entity modified in scope of the underlying transaction, passing the event data to it. If such an invocation is successful, an entity version is incremented in scope of the transaction.
